      "content": "i keep seeing something really weird on my bus ride to work. like, i saw the exact same guy in a red jacket walk past the window twice, but the timing was impossible... and then the trees in the park looked like they were repeating the same texture over and over. has anyone else ever noticed stuff like that? it feels like my eyes are tripping but it's too consistent.",
